Capitau’s Offer For Avusa Is Running Behind Schedule, Business Day Reports

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-06-22T05:32:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/capitau-s-offer-for-avusa-is-running-behind-schedule-business-day-reports.html
Capitau Holdings Ltd.’s bid to buy
and delist  Avusa Ltd. (AVU)  is behind schedule, with an agreement
required before due diligence not yet having been signed by
Capitau, Business Day reported, citing an unidentified person.  The due diligence has been put on hold pending further
negotiations, the Johannesburg-based newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  